parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inoperative seat belts can lead to serious injury or fatalities in the event of an accident, as they fail to provide proper restraint and protection to the occupants.
symptoms: Seat belts fail to tighten upon fast body movement or fast braking
intermittently lock up and do not move
fail to consistently grab when needed
and get stuck or jammed
making it difficult or impossible to use them.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to difficulty stopping the vehicle, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Brake master cylinder leaks
loss of brake fluid
difficulty stopping the vehicle
brakes lock up
vehicle skids.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS module can cause the brakes to lock up, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Brakes lock up
front wheels keep spinning
unable to find replacement ABS module.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Electrical Short in Steering Wheel and Brake/Turn Signal System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent electrical short can cause the fuse to blow, leading to the loss of braking lights and/or turn indicators, which can increase the risk of accidents and reduce vehicle safety.
symptoms: The fuse blows when using the turn signals and/or brakes
the vehicle is left without braking lights and/or turn indicators
the issue is intermittent and difficult to diagnose.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Adjustable Steering Wheel Electrical Connection
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty electrical connection in the adjustable steering wheel can cause an electrical short, leading to the loss of braking lights and/or turn indicators, which can increase the risk of accidents and reduce vehicle safety.
symptoms: The issue is intermittent
the fuse blows when using the turn signals and/or brakes
the vehicle is left without braking lights and/or turn indicators
the problem is related to the movement of the adjustable steering wheel.
